animal-produce.desc:
Non-dropped animal produce, like milk and wool.
Default: true
spawned-objects.desc:
Non-forage objects, like gems and minerals.
Default: true
tree-forage.desc:
Items from shaking trees, like seeds and Hazelnuts.
Default: true
mushroom-boxes.desc:
Works in any location.
Default: true
garbage-cans.desc:
Warning: Will cause lag when combined with Allow Global Collector.
Default: true
slime-balls.desc:
Slime Balls created by Slimes inside Slime Hutches.
Default: true
garden-pots.desc: Couples with Crops, Forage and Tea Bushes to determine what can be collected.
global-collector.desc:
Enables the use of the global Collector hotkey, which collects from every location. Also effects panning spots if enabled.
Warning: Will cause lag when combined with Garbage Cans.
Does not run on day start.
Default: false
global-collector.func-desc: Keybinds to manually perform global collection action.
inventory-anywhere.desc:
Enables the Open Collector Inventory hotkey, allowing access to the inventory from anywhere.
Default: false
shaving-enchant.desc:
Enables extra Hardwood collection from Stumps in the Secret Woods.
Amount extra depends on Upgrade Level setting.
Default: false
axe-upgrade-level.desc:
Determines how much extra Hardwood should be collected if Shaving is enabled.
Suggested to stay within the upgrade levels of tools.
Default: 1
fisher-enchant.desc:
Enabled panning spot collection to be able to collect fish.
Default: false
pan-arch-enchant.desc:
Increases chance to get Bone Fragments, artifacts and Artifact Troves from panning spots.
Default: false
pan-generous-enchant.desc:
Increases max amount of non-ore items from panning spots.
Amount extra depends on Upgrade Level setting.
Default: false
pan-upgrade-level.desc:
Used to determine chances of collecting extra items from panning spots.
Suggested to stay within the upgrade levels of tools.
Default: 1
hoe-arch-enchant.desc:
Doubles chance for artifacts in artifact spots.
Default: false
hoe-generous-enchant.desc:
Enables 50% chance of double yield from artifact spots.
Default: false
all-logging.desc:
Enables all console logging.
Default: false
collection-logging.desc:
Enables logging for primary Collector function.
Will not show panning collection that happens on time change.
Default: false
panning-logging.desc:
Enables logging for panning collection that occurs on time change.
Warning: this happens every time the in-game clock changes, it can get very spammy.
Default: false
informational-logging.desc:
Enables logging non-collection information such as location names with Collectors.
Default: false
verbose-logging.desc:
Enables always posting logs at Trace level, even when normal logging level is disabled.
Only enable if creating a log to send for support with the Collector mod.
Default: false
grabber-recipes.desc:
Recipes to convert from Auto-Grabber to Collector and back again.
Default: false
general-settings-info:
The following options require reloading a save to take effect.
They are best changed from the main menu.
special-orders.desc:
Enables special orders and events for the Collector recipe.
Default: true
run-day-start.desc:
Performs collection right after the day starts.
Default: true
run-day-end.desc:
Performs collection right before the day ends.
Default: true
